Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.35,0:00:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}这是 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是 是醉拳啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}从昨天电视中播的电影里看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.98,0:00:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哦哦 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.40,0:00:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}这借口编得跟麻耶一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.70,0:00:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}有好多拿着花的高中生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}今天是高中的毕业典礼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.48,0:00:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}话说回来 志愿该怎么填呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.84,0:00:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}已经到了不得不考虑的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:01:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}说到毕业典礼 心爱她…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.33,0:01:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}还没有毕业吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.01,0:01:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}能顺利升班吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是在担心这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我觉得没问题哟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我只是说说看而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.10,0:01:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃QAQ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.36,0:01:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真有问题啊！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}<OP>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}被毕业典礼感动到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}什么嘛 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.71,0:03:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}吓了我们一跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}而且 一想到我来到这个小镇如今已经快一年了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.27,0:03:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}时间真是转瞬即逝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 在这在这
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.56,0:03:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你怎么哭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你们是已经约好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 为了庆祝升班想开个茶会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}找到家不错的咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.33,0:03:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃你们也一起来怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}这难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}对别的店见异思迁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.28,0:03:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}要从Rabbit House毕业了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不是的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:03:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}满座了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}和高中生组的座位分开了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我也想像那样变得更加成熟些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.95,0:04:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}成熟些？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}像是对后辈说「一起去喝茶吧」这样自然的邀请她们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}能不能很自然的邀请到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那么惠 我们来试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.46,0:04:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}来吧来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}做得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那个 嗯哼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.59,0:04:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你 你真可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}一… 一起去喝茶怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}这是可疑的搭讪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哈哈哈哈～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}纱路喝茶的样子跟大小姐一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}感觉很成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我也想成为那样的高中生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.16,0:04:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}这个券还可以用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是免费券吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真是精打细算啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.33,0:05:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}令人憧憬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}这真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}总觉得妹妹好像被人抢走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是 是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}有没有成熟些了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}变得稍微优雅些了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.48,0:05:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}这是您的下午茶套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.35,0:05:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哦 好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.19,0:05:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我们没点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是那边的客人送的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}这里不是酒吧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嗯哼哼 看起来很高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}这是姐姐给可爱的妹妹们的礼物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}谢谢 心爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.25,0:05:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我开动……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我听说吃这些是有顺序的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.47,0:05:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.63,0:05:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好像是从三明治开始的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}还是司康饼来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.35,0:06:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那个 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}这要不吃出点样子来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就没法成为成熟的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}怎 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我们还是学学纱路她们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.95,0:06:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}在吃热狗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}这该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}对面也上来和我们一样的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}这是模仿的好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}盯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我感受到一股羡慕的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不 也许是我们正被观察着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}观察…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.27,0:06:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}观察我们是不是值得尊敬的前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}太夸张了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是吗 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你信了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.49,0:06:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你们觉得我对相对论的说明好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是想展现自己的脑袋顶呱呱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.04,0:07:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}要说到狭义相对论和广义相对论的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.78,0:07:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我比较喜欢狭义相对论
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}这话题竟然给接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}这 这年头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}把般若心经背下不过是小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}连纱路也来！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.03,0:07:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}果然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.09,0:07:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}广义
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}说到宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.31,0:07:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}狭义相对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.01,0:07:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}虽然搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不过应该是想在开吃之前好好聊一聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我们也得说些成熟的话题才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.10,0:07:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 最近我第一次让老哥去帮我跑腿了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.32,0:07:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}这哪里成熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.82,0:07:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}下 下次我就去Rabbit House的酒吧逛逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我 我就熬一下夜试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,0:07:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}姐姐我是不会允许的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}被听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}在喝下午茶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}看起来好欢乐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}青山小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.09,0:08:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}您知道这东西的吃法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}普通地吃不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}普通？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}对呀 普通地吃就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.56,0:08:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}青山小姐的普通估计和我们的不太一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}难道我很特殊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃她们在和青山小姐聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}话题好像挺严肃的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}她们肯定是在向青山小姐寻求意见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}关于什么的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.83,0:08:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}经过她们的观察觉得我们不值得尊敬什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}青山小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.64,0:08:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃她们要我来观察观察各位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}别说出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}相 相对论吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.85,0:08:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}狭义和广义和…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}色 色即是空 空 空即是色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:09:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我 我比较喜欢宇宙弦理论
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}呀 真巧 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}大 大家都这样吗 好巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我也是 我挺喜欢宇宙弦理论的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}因为不知道下午茶怎么喝才观察的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}呃 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.02,0:09:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}学着学着你的动作就跟到这里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}没必要这么钻牛角尖的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}可是 对于成熟的女性来说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}这些东西只要吃的开心就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}礼仪也只是为了让彼此更舒畅才存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}教官之训导 深入我心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 她们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:10:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}有空位子了所以拜托店员合并起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.80,0:10:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}锵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}用抽签来分位子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.05,0:10:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}可别为了自己和晚辈们坐一起出老千啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.88,0:10:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我可是很公平的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}人家光是能和大家一起开茶会就已经很高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}这个好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.94,0:10:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}来 智乃也吃吃呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嗯 也吃吃这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}只是分到了最远的座位而已嘛 别这么沮丧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好 好远啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我有个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}什么什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}尽管问
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}狭义相对论和广义相对论有什么区别
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.01,0:10:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}谁叫你们那么逞能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我要更努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嗯 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:10:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}再来再来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.98,0:11:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你到底想干啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我要变得更有姐姐样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃 我来帮你拿书包吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.08,0:11:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不 不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}和姐姐客气什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我没客气什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那我来背你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.46,0:11:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}客气什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}没客气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.39,0:11:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是姐姐寄来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.43,0:11:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}这次的回信速度好快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.93,0:11:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:12:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心爱 天亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.57,0:12:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.38,0:12:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心爱 就算是春假也不能睡懒觉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.69,0:12:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.15,0:12:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}玩偶！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}早安 智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}早饭要凉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}和平时不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.33,0:12:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}但是烧焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.17,0:12:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}用完早饭后　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我会告诉你狭义相对论和广义相对论之间的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.34,0:12:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.22,0:12:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心爱的样子很奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.31,0:13:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}的确
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.39,0:13:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}比平时更加机敏了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.77,0:13:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}这是在干啥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}摸提比也摸地更加机敏了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}揽客的动作也更机敏了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}带您入座
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.99,0:13:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好绅士～～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}搞得像别家店一样了 请别继续了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}这么一说和平时浏海的方向也反过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}可能是冒充的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.46,0:13:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}对了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}毛茸茸 毛茸茸 毛茸茸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}毛茸茸天国！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.39,0:13:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}这个应该还是会忍不住抱过来才对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不认真工作是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}虽然不知道为什么但是非常不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.34,0:13:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}微妙的受挫感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}如果努力过头发烧了就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.24,0:13:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我才刚这么想！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}为什么在这之前不说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}后天…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}后天？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}姐姐要过来…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.01,0:14:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}这有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.72,0:14:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就是说想让姐姐看到自己努力的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}要更加努力的去做才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.75,0:14:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}要好好的做智乃的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.03,0:14:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心爱的姐姐很严厉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}安心啦 很温柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}虽然我也有两个哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}但是姐姐教训他们 让他们听话的样子很帅的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}教训什么的 她是驯兽师吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}调教 我接下来会被怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.67,0:14:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}发抖了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.72,0:15:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}原来如此 所以才憧憬着姐姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.93,0:15:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}身为老幺也不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好 我来帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}让她看看你的优点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.98,0:15:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.32,0:15:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}但是 好羡慕心爱有那么多兄弟姐妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.53,0:15:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我是独生女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}理世
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}理世也要作为我的妹妹介绍给姐姐哦 和智乃一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.38,0:15:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}普通的朋友就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.71,0:15:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}姐姐修行？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}怎样才能看起来很可靠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.47,0:15:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我想让姐姐看到我的成长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就算你这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}总之 先让从刚才开始就抖个不停的智乃安下心来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.23,0:15:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\be3}要被揉个不停了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}没关系 有我陪着你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.78,0:15:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:16:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}没～关系 有我陪着你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:16:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\be3}住手 住手 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}明明是一样的台词 但差距这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.54,0:16:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}对了 理世你们稍微犯点蠢的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.29,0:16:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}这样就显得心爱很可靠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}逆向思考？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}但是 已经说了要帮助她了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}知道了 我试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦咦咦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那么 开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我想点餐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那个 咖 咖啡的种类我不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心爱 来帮忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我数学很烂 不小心订了一吨的罐装咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你这个冒失鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心爱 面包能用火焰喷射器烤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哇啊啊啊 我看不下去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.53,0:17:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}这可是为了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}接下来该换我们上场了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}请多指教 Sir！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心爱 这里还有灰尘哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.78,0:17:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}感觉有什么要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}这是婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}要接住这个飞盘哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}汪！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.41,0:17:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3\an8}好啦 我要扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.04,0:17:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}话说回来 这是什么的特训
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}因为想变得像姐姐一样 所以请模仿一下妹妹的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.58,0:17:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}OK
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}姐姐 我想吃面包
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.69,0:17:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我 我也
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}帮我做作业
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.43,0:17:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}一会就来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.68,0:17:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}这要持续到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}直到心爱察觉到这毫无意义为止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.40,0:18:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}今天谢谢大家为我忙这么久
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}几杯咖啡拿铁 不成敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 这是心爱画的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}比我第一次给我的时候进步多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}一直都在看反而没发现
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}这不就是你有在成长的证明吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.18,0:18:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心爱真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.47,0:18:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好棒好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好 今后我会更加发奋的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我想看3D咖啡拉花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.84,0:18:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.11,0:18:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.82,0:18:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就算作为店员进步了 作为姐姐也还差得很远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:18:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}3D咖啡拉花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.38,0:19:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}只是提比而已！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心爱真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.64,0:19:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不管过多久都成不了一个可靠的姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.56,0:19:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是吗？ 我觉得心爱已经是个很好的姐姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.44,0:19:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}虽说如此 但是光说不做出实际表现的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.11,0:19:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.74,0:19:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心爱一听说姐姐要来也太焦虑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}一般心不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.74,0:19:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.45,0:19:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃也是 明明近来跟心爱玩得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.29,0:19:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.79,0:19:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}纱路你是在担心心爱和智乃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.92,0:19:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我只是觉得心爱应该更自信一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.39,0:19:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那纱路也要拿出自信哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.73,0:20:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊？ 怎么说到我了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我很担心纱路你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}为什么要担心我啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}阔别一年的再会吗 应该很期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.03,0:20:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}又期待又担忧吧 连那个心爱都慌成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}作为姐姐的成长吗？ 真是自寻烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那种东西 只要是亲人 无须刻意展示也能感受得到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.26,0:20:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.35,0:20:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.39,0:20:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你偶尔也会说些正经话嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.10,0:20:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}这里也有个自大的儿子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.28,0:20:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}差不多到车站了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.33,0:21:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不去接真的好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.79,0:21:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}她信里说会自己来店里的 叫心爱专心工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.38,0:21:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是这样的吧？ 心爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.39,0:21:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心…爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.89,0:21:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心爱紧张得僵住了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.35,0:21:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}喂 你还得接客呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.55,0:21:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}信里不是叫你专心工作的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.71,0:21:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}喂 喂 心爱 没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.90,0:21:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\be3}心爱的姐姐…是个怎样的人呢？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.08,0:00:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}ED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.98,0:23:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}这下后果严重了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.31,0:23:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}具体有什么后果？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.88,0:23:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}这个嘛 反正很严重
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.38,0:23:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}很？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.05,0:23:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就是不得了的意思
